{"tid":2043681,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第一屆全球中文書法比賽 （香城學校主辦）","createTime":"2020-05-30T14:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T15:34:18.000Z","uid":266788,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"839c0753c8241900ad20a09effa07befdfa70db8","tid":2043681,"uid":266788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T14:52:03.000Z","msg":"英國保守黨既Benedict Rogers羅傑斯寫左&ldquo;齊上齊落&rdquo;畀香港人，係Twitter深受歡迎。再者，香港依家係全球焦點。小妹建議舉辦第一屆全球中文書法比賽，在國際宣傳香港，互勉互勵。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/15dWUPz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F15dWUPz.jpg&h=131f51d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/benedictrogers/status/1264591476736110598/photo/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbenedictrogers%2Fstatus%2F1264591476736110598%2Fphoto%2F1&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=ba922cf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbenedictrogers%2Fstatus%2F1264591476736110598%2Fphoto%2F1&h=292d3a9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/benedictrogers/status/1264591476736110598/photo/1</a><br />\n<br />\n全球書法比賽建議細節<br />\n1. 用紙筆寫 &ldquo;齊上齊落&rdquo; 四個正體中文字，字體不限（甲骨文，草書，行書，鬼劃符之類，你識咪寫）<br />\n2. 影相，放上Facebook, Twitter等social media<br />\n3. tag 3個人（最好係外國人台灣人奶茶聯盟成員），加一堆你鐘意既tag。<br />\n4. 要班鬼佬寫齊上齊落，再tag人<br />\n<br />\n靈感<br />\n近年d challenges多到不得了，tag下tag下就全世界一齊玩。<br />\n<br />\n2015年暑假，中大唔知邊個廢青係CUHK Secrets舉行書法比賽，中大上下一呼百應，笑料百出，成為2015暑假中大最受歡迎Secret活動之一。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K6spjgy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK6spjgy.jpg&h=1c8db9ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tf97g3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTf97g3e.jpg&h=f152ea16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3bH8LWA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3bH8LWA.jpg&h=3fe2d817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UgKnQog.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUgKnQog.jpg&h=c9e7694f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登以前都有搞到，幾多人玩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/4586/page/18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/4586/page/18</a><br />\n<br />\n目的/分析<br />\n1. 爭取更多國際支持，是次比賽無deadline，愈多人無時無刻參加就最好。呢四字對清晰易明，&ldquo;Face challenges together, overcome challenges together&rdquo;，唔只係support，更係solidarity/ togetherness 同在。希望各地既人與香港人同在，香港人都與世界受肺炎（所有左膠重視既problem又得）折磨既人同在。再者，呢四字看似好mild，但對香港人而言則係堅持既信念。係呢個時候，我地要更加爭取全球對香港人既solidarity。<br />\n2. 正面文宣，唔止香港極需要互相勉勵，外國好多地方都因為肺炎同lockdown好抑鬱，外國人圍內都好需要圍威喂，只不過係圍威喂期間團結香港。<br />\n3. 簡單又能挑戰。呢四隻字對鬼佬而言好似簡單又好似好難（睇返Rogers就知佢寫得有d吃力），呢d challenging but achievable既野先好玩，又可以當係lockdown娛樂。對奶茶聯盟而言，當練漢字。<br />\n4. 推廣正體中文<br />\n5. 滿足鬼佬對中華熱既慾望<br />\n6. 齊上齊落四字超positive，字面上完全冇野可以畀人challenge，即使係美國民主黨堆偽君子都唔怕得罪人，門檻極低。如果喺social media推得成，畀到香港人支持，外國人又互相支持，廢老又冇得話你班人搞亂香港<br />\n7. 平，一支筆一張廢紙only，唔似ALS又冰又水<br />\n<br />\n小妹好少出post，請畀建議及幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴日出過一次，有巴絲寫左好得意既&ldquo;齊上齊下&rdquo;，感謝你地。<br />\n原po: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2033627/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2033627/page/1</a><br />\n有冇得諗？！？！"},{"pid":"11abefddfd3a7ca3eac8968baa6a08647e9edac1","tid":2043681,"uid":266788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T14:53:05.000Z","msg":"愈多人參加愈好"},{"pid":"f740daf931427a96e16a5e0e242322fdb6198a49","tid":2043681,"uid":266788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T14:56:02.000Z","msg":"開錯台"},{"pid":"fd283327a4695da5f6bac09073caf0f805cd2067","tid":2043681,"uid":221055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T14:56:13.000Z","msg":"好玩，推"},{"pid":"91ea535f44b9b1011958f9049d2a4acf7d2a5327","tid":2043681,"uid":266788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T14:56:59.000Z","msg":"爭取民間支持"},{"pid":"cbcf8f391ae73fe5ec5c59a5cee9d428ea8ea6a0","tid":2043681,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T14:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be49f1da6eb2947943dee454d1bf9a5d9e30bf63","tid":2043681,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1628b6201fd684082cb246d5c2814bb60fbdf86","tid":2043681,"uid":223745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a975c3b16ae25b42241faa16dfc30adaa0504a0e","tid":2043681,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6056eec9b321fc2a9ddb1fad83de2f7369bd21","tid":2043681,"uid":263018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:21:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"381bead650ab96caec794ad22ffd42e0ece569b5","tid":2043681,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}